   against the public’s right to be informed

   Supporters in France have “image rights” too. Usually, it is the image
   rights of footballers and their exploitation by clubs or the media that
   are the subject of disputes and court cases. However, the judgment of
   the Court of Appeal of Versailles dated 7 May 2019 (no. 17/03549),
